snippet.title: Suicide Squad Song | Voices In My Head | NerdOut ft. Emily Amber (Unofficial Soundtrack)
snippet.description:
Suicide Squad song is finally here! This is a very different project to what we usually do, but the movie was so good, I'm glad we did something for it. I hope you like this different style of song and if you do, let us know what movies you would like to see an unofficial soundtrack to! It would really mean a lot if you left a like on this and shared it with friends! You can also buy this song on iTunes & stream it on Spotify

🎵 Listen on Spotify, Apple Music, Amazon and more! 🎵
